{"tid":1766554,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"(求救重開) 第一次求人 求下大家幫下我","createTime":"2019-12-02T16:13:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-04T16:34:51.000Z","uid":140912,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"62bc7fc4e25b7f78f20174f7451002f7daa98092","tid":1766554,"uid":140912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T16:13:28.000Z","msg":"(求救)經過呢幾個月 我覺得我真係有抑鬱症<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1764051\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1764051</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n呢個係我早幾日開既post<br />\n想開多次係因為我試過大家畀我嘅方法<br />\ntg果d link都有搵過<br />\n但好多冇覆/話我既情況冇得義診<br />\n我知我冇用但我真係連診金都唔夠。。。<br />\n唔好誤會 我唔係要上嚟呃錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我之前既錢 一係捐左一係拎曬去買60926派<br />\n突然冇咗份工真係搞唔掂 只僅僅夠錢開飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我只係想問下如果有人有類似嘅情況 <br />\n或者有睇開醫生嘅 可唔可以畀幾粒藥我食下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我可以自己試多幾隻睇下有冇效<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我真係唔掂先上黎問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n失眠好多晚 尋晚終於瞓到一隔<br />\n點知發惡夢見到自己比人凌遲處死<br />\n見到成身都係血俾人一忽一忽肉割落黎<br />\n醒咗全身都係汗 個人不停震左好耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有冇人可以幫幫我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b4a6740e4cb0c28d828ed8a64bacbd7d39fce30","tid":1766554,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T16:15:01.000Z","msg":"push<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n[黃色經濟圈] 時代革命由生活開始：黃色商圈已降臨（劉細良）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1766519\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1766519</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"8a1df11d2efa2704fca51bafd2a0443e094fc28e","tid":1766554,"uid":140912,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T16:15:28.000Z","msg":"我唔記得咗揀台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n本身想開係健康台 但手快快出左<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔係吹緊水係認真問大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34a5242e644baaabc5d2d568447c6bcf540f5924","tid":1766554,"uid":140912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T16:16:41.000Z","msg":"自推下:"},{"pid":"5345dc9876dd5f43e7b59e9859ff7dd757cd4c88","tid":1766554,"uid":36391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T16:17:38.000Z","msg":"推一推"},{"pid":"a32e1e36b104d508b705c04bdb8f0b3088ba64e7","tid":1766554,"uid":140912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T16:19:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/22.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03479cca70711a4847434d92a77ef5b38806f4fc","tid":1766554,"uid":140912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T16:21:24.000Z","msg":"垃圾自推1/10"},{"pid":"9ac79a63f35e663c59ec3405ca26606e9a4d0a76","tid":1766554,"uid":140912,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T16:21:36.000Z","msg":"垃圾自推2/10"},{"pid":"8976ddd4ef991c86c75bbad0c10dce3bc061f814","tid":1766554,"uid":140912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T16:21:46.000Z","msg":"垃圾自推3/10"},{"pid":"19532bffa91e898372b6110727c458a25bd7e497","tid":1766554,"uid":140912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T16:22:09.000Z","msg":"垃圾自推4/10"},{"pid":"f62cf616b0adf1555f42d075c15a41f1d7dc650c","tid":1766554,"uid":140912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T16:23:00.000Z","msg":"垃圾自推5/10"},{"pid":"dc207ac24a22e103cb3dc81eebd2715af5c18e9a",