edBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T16:35:36.000Z","msg":"一推"},{"pid":"3294978b4b547ccd64710ae56d88ad84fee3f784","tid":1766554,"uid":167330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T16:36:37.000Z","msg":"二推<br />\n<br />\n樓主如果個po沉咗唔好介意推，或者開新po，呢到好多巴打樂意聽你傾訴，唔好唔好意思<br />\n<br />\n始終呢排咁多po好易沉"},{"pid":"5d14b041c71c94cfb6260eb97a5090f98160071b","tid":1766554,"uid":86400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T16:38:12.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"f1247717b7c8ba8bb1fdb8bfe513c01c9c4e5341","tid":1766554,"uid":37870,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5a1f570a03f8cd00514757473f123c93125e6fa6","tid":1766554,"uid":140912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T16:35:05.000Z","msg":"精神狀態好差冇動力做任何嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T16:38:15.000Z","msg":"你一定要行出第一步，你先廿歲仔<br />\n朋友藍咪搵過，屋企藍咪返工有錢搬出去<br />\n世界冇左邊個唔得"},{"pid":"2ed497aea53ec2b6aa12030cbd641aaa6422ebfc","tid":1766554,"uid":167330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T16:39:03.000Z","msg":"三推<br />\n<br />\n我都係好易抑鬱嘅人，唔開心嘅時候會匿埋唔出街見人，但咁樣反而搞到惡性循環，出去見下朋友，或者搵個靜靜嘅地方瞓低思考都唔錯"},{"pid":"6bdcc0e6365698c62c0ad47ba63599b7a908ac84","tid":1766554,"uid":37870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f1247717b7c8ba8bb1fdb8bfe513c01c9c4e5341","tid":1766554,"uid":37870,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5a1f570a03f8cd00514757473f123c93125e6fa6","tid":1766554,"uid":140912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T16:35:05.000Z","msg":"精神狀態好差冇動力做任何嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T16:38:15.000Z","msg":"你一定要行出第一步，你先廿歲仔<br />\n朋友藍咪搵過，屋企藍咪返工有錢搬出去<br />\n世界冇左邊個唔得"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T16:39:43.000Z","msg":"同埋你唔太擅長社交，有錢嗰陣養返隻貓或者狗，不過記得領養<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd28674e251cb31a5796b1d60506cb258ca1034a","tid":1766554,"uid":219128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T16:40:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2eaeca31d492c05d3619125fdab79607bf29597","tid":1766554,"uid":56043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T16:41:32.000Z","msg":"欣賞你察覺到自己的異樣和願意主動向外界求助<br />\n但呢到剖白自己始終唔係最好既方法。<br />\n願意尋找輔導嗎？  社工？ 輔導員？ 或者去最近既綜合家庭服務中心，評估下有無抑鬱先？<br />\n<br />\n始終連登唔係一個評估好地方，亦難以準確量度"},{"pid":"46085d83561eda97dbbce7f441e57142597cf4f4","tid":1766554,"uid":140912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2ed497aea53ec2b6aa12030cbd641aaa6422ebfc","tid":1766554,"uid":167330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T16:39:03.000Z","msg":"三推<br />\n<br />\n我都係好易抑鬱嘅人，唔開心嘅時候會匿埋唔出街見人，但咁樣反而搞到惡性循環，出去見下朋友，或者搵個靜靜嘅地方瞓低思考都唔錯"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T16:43:21.000Z","msg":"多謝你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 祝你有好多個大波妹屌到退休<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"152b3f8dc0e8c130b792c024421d98ec8c15cfcf","tid":1766554,"uid":140912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6bdcc0e6365698c62c0ad47ba63599b7a908ac84","tid":1766554,"uid":37870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f1247717b7c8ba8bb1fdb8bfe513c01c9c4e5341","tid":1766554,"uid":37870,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5a1f570a03f8cd00514757473f123c93125e6fa6","tid":1766554,"uid":140912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T16:35:05.000Z","msg":"精神狀態好差冇動力做任何嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T16:38:15.000Z","msg":"你一定要行出第一步，你先廿歲仔<br />\n朋友藍咪搵過，屋企藍咪返工有錢搬出去<br />\n世界冇左邊個唔得"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T16:39:43.000Z","msg":"同埋你唔太擅長社交，有錢嗰陣養返隻貓或者狗，不過記得領養<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T16:44:09.000Z","msg":"一直都好鍾意貓狗但係屋企人唔畀我養<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我都覺得我好需要有個心靈寄託<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff1bce9087c889273b3002f910676b23a42e665b","tid":1766554,"uid":140912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d2eaeca31d492c05d3619125fdab79607bf29597","tid":1766554,"uid":56043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T16:41:32.000Z","msg":"欣賞你察覺到自己的異樣和願意主動向外界求助<br />\n但呢到剖白自己始終唔係最好既方法。<br />\n願意尋找輔導嗎？  社工？ 輔導員？ 或者去最近既綜合家庭服務中心，評估下有無抑鬱先？<br />\n<br />\n始終連登唔係一個評估好地方，亦難以準確量度"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T16:45:24.000Z","msg":"又搵過佢哋 評估咗我係抑鬱加焦慮<br />\n但如果要睇醫生或者要食藥嘅要轉介同埋診金每次咁比好貴下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4833128814214baf04fb60c29b8e768bd4a70aef","tid":1766554,"uid":311819,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T16:49:20.000Z","msg":"迫自己做運動 發洩出黎<br />\n跑下圈 咩都好 出身汗個人會好啲<br />\n極發你個腦輸出多巴胺<br />\n你跑完你個人會有種成功感<br />\n10分鐘嘅運動已經對你身體有益<br />\n當然唔好格硬黎 慢慢跑 無氣嘅停下先 飲下水咁<br />\n唔好諗你跑步差過人點點點 淨係跑唔好理人點諗 阿甘咁係咁跑 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n樓主加油<br />\n運動係最好嘅良藥<br />\n記得要食正餐<br />\n<br />\n過來人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62bb148f0ad87157737988656eb5fb6189a9838c","tid":1766554,"uid":76427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T16:55:04.000Z","msg":"用過來人身份認真答你 儘管試下冇壞<br />\n1. 做運動<br />\n2. 玩下小動物 eg 去下貓cafe<br />\n3. 之前睇醫生教 開本簿寫低自己腦海中浮現既野 整理下思緒個人會冇咗亂 文筆好既可以試下寫作<br />\n仲有可以寫低每日值得開心既三件事 e.g.今日飲咗珍珠奶茶 不過呢樣要慢慢黎 一開始諗唔到會仲燥底/覺得生無可戀 要個人思緒冇咁亂先發掘到身邊美好既事物<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後 預咗被屌都要講 雖然我唔建議隨便試<br />\n食煙係有用過食藥 但心理同生理健康自己取捨"},{"pid":"a03c441cfe579922db50b094911775aa41007a29","tid":1766554,"uid":76427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T16:56:49.000Z","msg":"唔記得講 巴打加油捱落去 煲底見個時俾個擁抱你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c63365996bac89a4359976a37a0519b8be3a62e2","tid":1766554,"uid":81478,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T17:17:10.000Z","msg":"樓主可以試下搵返份pt返住先<br />\n可能一個星期返3/4日<br />\n其他日子就做下運動 打下機 比自己放鬆下<br />\n等情況穩定啲先會返多啲工etc<br />\n<br />\n呢場運動幫你認清身邊啲人<br />\n好似&rsquo;兄弟&rsquo;咁冇咗係好可惜 <br />\n但你地價值觀都唔同嘅時候 點叫兄弟？<br />\n女朋友同樣 <br />\n加上大把前線&amp;後勤絲啦<br />\n留返煲底相見嗰日再慢慢識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n記住你好重要㗎！<br />\n少你一個少好多 <br />\n情緒唔掂嘅時候諗下我地<br />\n背後仲有一大班人㗎！<br />\n約咗煲底相見㗎嘛 唔準失約呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b0feae703978f538a550910e0792f5890d2f2df","tid":1766554,"uid":193972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T01:44:06.000Z","msg":"試下甘麥大棗湯:<br />\n<a href=\"https://kknews.cc/zh-tw/health/y8qgnzk.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fkknews.cc%2Fzh-tw%2Fhealth%2Fy8qgnzk.html&d=r4%2BjDf%2BCRrsm4RwUuvkwRYLj0gigvT8yTat38OYNh6E%3D&h=e1d993c2\" target=\"_blank\">https://kknews.cc/zh-tw/health/y8qgnzk.html</a><br />\n簡單甘草浮小麥同大棗每樣手執一把煲一公升水滾一陣焗下就飲得, 當茶水咁飲, 飲完會好瞓同冇夢<br />\n瞓得好, 情緒會好好多"},{"pid":"7b167240fdca05576dbeb572f2178b2592dd9372","tid":1766554,"uid":56043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ff1bce9087c889273b3002f910676b23a42e665b","tid":1766554,"uid":140912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d2eaeca31d492c05d3619125fdab79607bf29597","tid":1766554,"uid":56043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T16:41:32.000Z","msg":"欣賞你察覺到自己的異樣和願意主動向外界求助<br />\n但呢到剖白自己始終唔係最好既方法。<br />\n願意尋找輔導嗎？  社工？ 輔導員？ 或者去最近既綜合家庭服務中心，評估下有無抑鬱先？<br />\n<br />\n始終連登唔係一個評估好地方，亦難以準確量度"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T16:45:24.000Z","msg":"又搵過佢哋 評估咗我係抑鬱加焦慮<br />\n但如果要睇醫生或者要食藥嘅要轉介同埋診金每次咁比好貴下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T02:52:00.000Z","msg":"佢哋同你評估嗰個社工，或者嗰個機構，有冇同你開case跟進？佢哋應該會提供個案輔導嘅服務啦，就算冇約呢佢哋都會有跟進或者轉介㗎。 <br />\n<br />\n另外你亦都可以去返自己地區嘅醫院聯網，普通科嗰隻，俗稱街症，同返醫生講有呢個問題，56 蚊一次好似，佢就會轉介你，但你預咗政府專科就要等時間囉....佢會跟你嗰個急切性去處理"},{"pid":"91165a1c3954b934272dc1698e6b1c2b1e11b643","tid":1766554,"uid":108910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T03:03:16.000Z","msg":"樓主還好嘛？"},{"pid":"c2777b8560353552ad5aa74f40147f8f02a9e2a6","tid":1766554,"uid":37870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T04:30:12.000Z","msg":"樓主係訓左咋？"},{"pid":"734597302eefe82cb3b4304f24fe4ec1314240aa","tid":1766554,"uid":70745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T13:35:38.000Z","msg":"唔好有事呀唔該"},{"pid":"c266e854b2ae7bf7ff5a77bae2de796f5bd140e6","tid":1766554,"uid":183844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T13:58:32.000Z","msg":"「重開」又有香港人失蹤<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1755555\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1755555</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n有個 tg 失蹤人士channel<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/FindingHKer\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FFindingHKer&d=r4%2BjDf%2BCRrsm4RwUuvkwRYLj0gigvT8yTat38OYNh6E%3D&h=dc17b126\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/FindingHKer</a><br />\n<br />\nfb group<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/434115767233839/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2F434115767233839%2F&d=r4%2BjDf%2BCRrsm4RwUuvkwRYLj0gigvT8yTat38OYNh6E%3D&h=ecdc2280\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/434115767233839/</a><br />\n<br />\n￼大家仲記唔記得<br />\n太子站搵朋友個姨姨？<br />\n<br />\n831 搵失蹤姨姨 (之後有「認罪」錄音)<br />\n［勁恐怖］太子站前上鏡受訪問後<br />\n被逼錄音同可能已被自殺<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1577080\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1577080</a>"},{"pid":"17354a8c7c60053dc4a9002ee1cab709f9ec0bff","tid":1766554,"uid":303115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"152b3f8dc0e8c130b792c024421d98ec8c15cfcf","tid":1766554,"uid":140912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6bdcc0e6365698c62c0ad47ba63599b7a908ac84","tid":1766554,"uid":37870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f1247717b7c8ba8bb1fdb8bfe513c01c9c4e5341","tid":1766554,"uid":37870,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T16:38:15.000Z","msg":"你一定要行出第一步，你先廿歲仔<br />\n朋友藍咪搵過，屋企藍咪返工有錢搬出去<br />\n世界冇左邊個唔得"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T16:39:43.000Z","msg":"同埋你唔太擅長社交，有錢嗰陣養返隻貓或者狗，不過記得領養<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T16:44:09.000Z","msg":"一直都好鍾意貓狗但係屋企人唔畀我養<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我都覺得我好需要有個心靈寄託<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T15:31:09.000Z","msg":"努力啲行出第一步<br />\n搵份工有份糧先有底氣搬出黎住，到時養貓狗陪自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n加油啊巴打 香港人需要你"},{"pid":"590d12f278336c181328d0fb72e358dfb680ef81","tid":1766554,"uid":37870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T16:11:03.000Z","msg":"樓主上下水好喎"},{"pid":"3a894cc8b97c08295fb45b105022b6e5ad483f76","tid":1766554,"uid":111028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T16:13:43.000Z","msg":"做多啲鐘意做嘅事<br />\n搵人陪你放鬆下啦"},{"pid":"7f35112f327bd8eb34ae14afc92249268b9a0261","tid":1766554,"uid":269202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T16:16:15.000Z","msg":"精神科藥物效果完左會反擊你<br />\n你係咪被拘留過？"},{"pid":"1b815556afc10f04f0ee04c6faf9a094f4a3aa09","tid":1766554,"uid":120537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T16:20:38.000Z","msg":"- 政府普通科門診 -&gt; 轉介專科<br />\n- 搵信得過嘅社工/輔導<br />\n- 做運動<br />\n- 落下公園去下郊野公園，wallpaper換大自然風景<br />\n- 學下meditation，聽落好似好難/宗教嘢咁，其實基本上只係專心呼吸"},{"pid":"8e08b1575bdcbf845551f311c4d76c4c9269c184","tid":1766554,"uid":183844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T16:33:51.000Z","msg":"加油呀手足"},{"pid":"0399599f4e0bdb37ffd603296bbd5d4fc4b9c4ea","tid":1766554,"uid":234219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T16:35:34.000Z","msg":"幫你唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唯有幫你推下"},{"pid":"104db6436b2d4ac1b0bbb82c529af4ff934f9a65","tid":1766554,"uid":70745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T16:36:36.000Z","msg":"樓主重新開po keep住報平安pls"},{"pid":"19b65b8d7f0d11c767f528660d4c1b1213f6d71d","tid":1766554,"uid":332877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T16:39:07.000Z","msg":"樓主記得上一上水報平安先"},{"pid":"bed13f394e88be467f92037c15e573aca84eb357","tid":1766554,"uid":12248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T16:40:11.000Z","msg":"樓主報平安阿<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c516ae519e82357bb6aec31b16f54b1ee9987a88","tid":1766554,"uid":29138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T16:43:14.000Z","msg":"哦 舊post繼續討論？<br />\n<blockquote>屌鳩晒你地 快撚啲眾籌比樓主 唔撚籌就係殺人兇手！<br />\n萬一無人幫手得個講字 樓主記得寫定遺書寫埋lihkg id 等等 <br />\n等我地可以Fc <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔洗黑警亂殺人又入錯數<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/14.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n希望樓主睇到！黑警死全家 來生永遠做中國人抱擁大灣區<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},